node.text:
Our new Miscellaneous Collection!🧸🛋
This collection is a series of fun, beautiful, and incredibly hard household items. Even including our two brand mascots, Hard Willy & Hell The Hound. All pieces made by us, the Hard Jewelry team. It took a little bit more than a year to perfect each piece- and although each piece isn't perfect, it is an accurate representation of the hard jewelry experience. Hard and fun.... Pause.... Resume... I hope you enjoy🖤 

Our Miscellaneous Collection will be releasing on March 26th @ 8 p.m. MTN time🙂🖤

node.text:
Not to downplay therapy especially in times like this that we’re in... But your HJ will never leave you.

Your HJ is a constant reminder that no matter how hard life gets, you’re never alone.

When you let somebody else wear your HJ, it is a constant reminder to them that they’re important and worthy of such love and drip. Not to mention your HJ will last a lifetime.

That’s why jewelry is such a good gift.
But I digress.

Your Hard Jewelry is more than just jewelry. It is a symbol of hope and love in this unforgiving world.
